a divokým zvieraťom]</i>

79
00:08:39,090 --> 00:08:41,290
- Vojaci!
- Vojaci!

80
00:08:41,990 --> 00:08:44,590
- Chyťte ich!
- Chyťte ich!

81
00:08:48,290 --> 00:08:50,190
Prečo si bežal?

82
00:08:50,190 --> 00:08:52,790
